{"tid":2149784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【守護新聞自由】買《蘋果》 一齊撐 #WeNeedAppleDaily","createTime":"2020-08-10T14:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T05:18:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"88e7c35ec81cef234e6cb5c709150293fbd74dea","tid":2149784,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:52:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/7G4KVIQKSF2FHHXQINEFEL26FI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2F7G4KVIQKSF2FHHXQINEFEL26FI%2F&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=3c726da4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2F7G4KVIQKSF2FHHXQINEFEL26FI%2F&h=7eb16a69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/7G4KVIQKSF2FHHXQINEFEL26FI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Vg805mp6TgbVenrl8bfgAaYjubQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G7VWZEHQOVG6OLE76JWPYLYCVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVg805mp6TgbVenrl8bfgAaYjubQ%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG7VWZEHQOVG6OLE76JWPYLYCVQ.jpg&h=3aade334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政權越打壓，我們越頑強。前路越黑暗，我們越要守住那點光。《蘋果日報》今日（10日）面對創刊25周年以來最嚴峻打壓，警方以《國安法》之名拘捕壹傳媒多名高層、大舉搜查整間報館，連編採部採訪資料亦被肆意翻閱，記者協會形容香港新聞自由遭嚴重踐踏，國際城市淪落至連第三世界國家都不如。<br />\n<br />\n不過，《蘋果》已沒有後退空間，即使報館滿佈荷槍警員，封鎖線遍佈辦公室每個角落，蘋果人仍無懼威嚇、緊守崗位，繼續以文字守護真相，用出版捍衞自由。我們努力撐住，亦靠你們以行動支持。請讀者明早購買一份《蘋果日報》，並拿着《蘋果》拍照，再上載至自己的社交網站，包括Facebook、Instagram和Twitter，再標註「#撐蘋果日報」、「#SupportAppleDaily」及「#WeNeedAppleDaily」。<br />\n<br />\n也許《蘋果》從來不討人喜愛，但連《蘋果》都守不住，還談何新聞自由。香港人，一起撐住。"},{"pid":"1d6c58cdde1e027ffcd81ca58194204ced2de507","tid":2149784,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:55:16.000Z